column1: January 2018 ASP NOC NDC - HCPCS Crosswalk for Medicare Part B Drugs
Note 1: This crosswalk is based on published drug and biological pricing data and information submitted to CMS by manufacturers. The information is
intended to support  ASP-based Medicare Part B payments only.
Note 2: Please submit comments on the crosswalk to e-mail address: sec303aspdata@cms.hhs.gov.
